org.activebpel.rt.bpel.wsio.invoke
Class AeWSIInvokeHandlerBase

java.lang.Object
  org.activebpel.rt.bpel.wsio.invoke.AeWSIInvokeHandlerBase
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAeInvokeHandler
public abstract class AeWSIInvokeHandlerBase
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAeInvokeHandler

Base class for custom invoke handlers that handle invokes to WSI compliant services. This base class expects a single part input message. The operation name is used to look up a method that implements that operation (using reflection).
